Tenei tau i runga i tenei mata whakamahia ki te hanga i tētahi rōpū motuhake o ngā kaiwhakamahi. Te arotake i te tau i runga i ngā mata kaiwhakamahi katoa \', ka e tae ngā kaiwhakamahi katoa te maha i raro taua, me te pēhi OK.
Na, me taurite ki a koe tetahi o enei kupui lea 3-kupu ki ngā kaiwhakamahi katoa. Me tīpako i nga kaiwhakamahi i te kīanga noa taua, ka pēhi whai mai.
